<HEADLINE>
MAKING A DENT IN THE DEMAND FOR ILLEGAL DRUGS 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 By ALAN FEUER   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
