Committee (IOC) held its 103rd annual session. One subject of
discussion was whether to name the relatively young sport triathlon
to the Summer Olympic program as a medal sport. The decision was
yes and with the 2000 Summer Games approaching, we can look forward
to witnessing an iconic display of athleticism and determination
when triathlon makes its Olympic debut in Sydney, Australia.
(Dayton Daily News) 22. WITH PHOTOS. MOVED.
