<P>
   What's your handicap? Find out here
</P>
<P>
   Although your findings won't be considered by the USGA as an
official handicap (those will cost you), weekend golfers can
calculate an unofficial handicap at this site. It helps you monitor
your rounds, including fairways hit, driving distance, putts and
other pertinent information. And it's free.
</P>
<P>
   www.nethandicap.com
