   TOP
</P>
<P>
   Lead story:
</P>
<P>
   U.N.-SUMMIT-CLINTON (Undated) _ A look at President Clinton's
plans for the summit at the United Nations. By David E. Sanger. (We
plan to move the story by 8:30 p.m. ET in ``i'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   With general summit photos, NYT4,5.
</P>
<P>
   Top center: 3-column photo reefer to NY-WEST-INDIAN-DAY; story
inside Metro.
</P>
<P>
   Off-lead story:
</P>
<P>
   FLIGHT-DELAYS (Undated) _ Labor Day marks the end of the second
