five years, he has run run a small venture capital firm with his
two brothers. It is his way of fulfilling a desire to work with his
family -- and to help proselytize about the virtues of the Internet
without suffering the corporate intrigue that overwhelmed him at
both Apple and at Spectrum Information Technologies. By Hilary
