<P>
   BRITAIN: LAWMAKER TO QUIT
</P>
<P>
   Mo Mowlam, the former Northern Ireland secretary whose
popularity among the Labor Party faithful with the public has
regularly exceeded that of Prime Minister Tony Blair, said she
